body.description: Dove Men+Care Clinical Protection Clean Comfort Antiperspirant Stick gives you 96h sweat protection while caring for sensitive skin. This antiperspirant stick is formulated with 1/4 Moisturizing Cream to help retain skin moisture and help protect against irritation for more comfortable underarms. This Clinical Strength antiperspirant features a long-lasting subtle fragrance to keep you feeling fresh and confident all day. Simply apply this clinical strength antiperspirant in an even layer onto each of your underarms to help soothe and protect your underarms from sweat and odor for lasting confidence around the clock. Looking for more Dove Men+Care skin care products? Try the full range of Dove Men+Care products, including antiperspirant deodorants, dry spray antiperspirant deodorants, body washes, face and body bars, and other hair and skin care products. Each Dove Men+Care antiperspirant stick can be recycled. Follow the How2Recycle instructions on the back. All Dove products, including this antiperspirant deodorant, are PETA-certified cruelty-free. Globally, Dove does not test on animals.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Dove Men+Care Clinical Protection Clean Comfort Antiperspirant keeps you dry and fresh with 72-hour protection. This antiperspirant deodorant with an invigorating citrus scent features a unique Triple Action Moisturizer to protect against skin irritation.

CLINICAL-STRENGTH PROTECTION This antiperspirant provides powerful sweat protection to keep you feeling fresh and dry. SUPERIOR CARE Our unique Triple Action Moisturizer nourishes and protects underarms for healthier skin that’s less prone to irritation. FRESH FRAGRANCE The soft linen scent provides long-lasting freshness and confidence. DESIGNED FOR YOUR COMFORT Stay cool and fresh with our full range of Dove Men+Care Clean Comfort skin care products designed for your needs.

Dove Men+Care Clean Comfort Antiperspirant Stick Dove Men+Care Clean Comfort Dry Spray Antiperspirant Dove Men+Care Clean Comfort Body and Face Bar Main Benefit This antiperspirant stick protects against sweat and odor for 48 hours. This antiperspirant spray helps fight sweat and odor for up to 48 hours. Dove Men+Care Clean Comfort Body and Face Bar helps maintain your skin’s hydration levels and leaves skin feeling cleansed and comfortable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works really well, but there is another
reviews.reviewText: This deodorant works very well; however, there is another deodorant that works just as well, doesn't run out as fast, significantly cheaper, and smells better.Mitchum Triple Odor Defense 48 HourTo be fair, the Dove is quite nice. It glides on a lot smoother due to its fluffy consistency, but this causes it to run out in about 2 weeks. The Dove does smell nice, but the wife likes the Mitchum more. The Dove says 96 hour protection though I did not experience more than 24 hours, which is the same experience I have with the Mitchum.This is my opinion. I know which one I am going to continue to buy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works well. Doesn't give me a rash.
reviews.reviewText: When my old deodorant was discontinued, I had a rough time finding one that didn't make my armpits breakout in a rash. This is the only one I found that also was an anti-perspirant. Overall, it works great. I highly recommend if you have sensitive skin.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My favorite for sensitive skin
reviews.reviewText: This has a nice, fresh scent and does not irritate my underarms like a lot of products do. For best results apply after an evening shower before bedtime. Doing this lasts me all the next day although I have not tested the 96 hour claim.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Deodorant that actually works.
reviews.reviewText: Been using it for years, can't find anything better.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 23, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolutely lives up to its name…
reviews.reviewText: This product far exceeded my expectations. Keeps you drier than other brands. The scent is extremely light, not cloying in any way at all. The anti-perspirant continues to work even after showering. The thin layer of stuff (sticky layer) remains for up to two or three days, but when you shower, of course, the body odor is removed. Allowing you to use this at night before bed. Allow it to dry.. and then the next morning, one can choose a non-antiperspirant with a better scent, because the anti… is still active for you. Worked from the first time i used it… even though i walked in ninety five degree heat. Of course your going to sweat, but not like before. And then after the second time i used it, i could alternate between this product and the better smelling Sam’s deoderant’s such as cedar etc etc.. when the sweat started to become something to deal with again, i once more applied this product before bed as instructions state to do. Ad infinitum … well worth the money. One also does not need to rub this in back and forth in ridiculous amounts. Use a thin layer, once up one side of the “pit”… down the other. And that’s all you need to do. It does NOT destroy one’s clothing with stains either. Perfect companion for summer heat. Will definitely recommend to others. As well as recommend people read the instructions on an anti-perspirant so it will work best. Who knew most of us were applying these wrong for so long? Lol

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars An antiperspirant with zero irritation
reviews.reviewText: I swore off antiperspirants for a few years due to the pain I would experience on and around my armpits after applying it, instead opting to use deodorant. Lately the deodorant hasn’t been doing the job as well as I would like, so I thought I’d shop around and give antiperspirants another shot.With this product, I experience zero armpit irritation. It’s only been three days, so things could change, but currently this product works amazingly well. 5/5

reviews.reviewTitle: it is good. It delivers what it promises
reviews.reviewText: Delivery of product took a little more time than expected but it still was within the stipulated time period. I guess this was because they import it from the US.As for the product, it is good. It delivers what it promises. I use it once every morning and it lasts through the day. It does sometime leave some residue on the clothing adjacent to one's armpit, but it doesn't stain it and doesn't show. Strongly recommended
